Notes: WIAC Quarterfinals...SP advances to semifinals for third straight year and
will host game on Wed. at 7 pm...SP led 26-21 with six minutes left in first
half and closed half with 24-4 run... UWL came no closer than 21 points in
second half...SP's Hodgson tied career high with 13 points.
Game.Officials: Blaine Hilgendorf,  Michelle Miller,  Ron Quirk
